OL,3,CCrowds give bedbound veteran, 86,
OL,4,Cmilitary surprise at care home
OL,6,FHundreds of bikers, veterans and
OL,7,Flocals from a village in North have
OL,8,Fcome together for a special surprise
OL,9,Fof a lifetime for one care home
OL,10,Fresident.
OL,12,FCharlie Drinkwater, 86, served in the
OL,13,FGrenadier Guards 3rd Battalion between
OL,14,F1957 and 1959 and when care home staff
OL,15,Fin Brigg asked him what his one wish
OL,16,Fwas he said to meet more veterans like
OL,17,Fhim.
OL,19,FAfter a plea was posted on social
OL,20,Fmedia, hundreds of people turned up to
OL,21,Fvisit him on Sunday.
