OL,3,CCrowds give bedbound veteran, 86,
OL,4,Cmilitary surprise at care home
OL,6,FCharlie described the day as "spot on."
OL,8,FHis daughter Fiona Esberger said:
OL,9,F"It's absolutely amazing,
OL,10,Funbelievable. his passion in life has
OL,11,Fbeen motorbikes and of course the time
OL,12,Fhe served in the military. This has
OL,13,Fbrought the two together so it's just
OL,14,Fwonderful for him."
OL,16,FA military band and bagpipers were
OL,17,Famong the hundreds of people who
OL,18,Farrived at Wrawby Hall Care Home.
OL,20,FThere was also a contingent of bikers
OL,21,Fas Charlie loves motorbikes.
