OL,3,CCrowds give bedbound veteran, 86,
OL,4,Cmilitary surprise at care home
OL,6,FDanielle Savage from the care home
OL,7,Fsaid: "Charlie started talking about
OL,8,Fhis time in the forces. And we felt,
OL,9,Fbecause he was speaking about it so
OL,10,Fpassionately, that we had to do
OL,11,Fsomething with that.
OL,13,F"I know there's people coming from the
OL,14,FGrenadier Guards, from all different
OL,15,Fareas of the forces, and it's bringing
OL,16,Fthem all together. It's something that
OL,17,Ffor many many years hopefully people
OL,18,Fwill remember."
